    "questionText": "A client asks you to audit a workshop. You need to measure the electrical pressure (voltage) entering the building, the instantaneous rate of power being used by the machinery, and the total energy consumed by the workshop over a full week. Name the three specific instruments you would use for these three measurements in the order they were mentioned.",
